    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i really don't want to go to the hospital if i don't have to. the doctors always make such a big deal out of everything and it just spikes my anxiety even more. is there any way i can just take something to calm down and see if the feeling goes away? like maybe some extra benadryl or something to help me sleep through the heaviness?",
